ConditionalRule - Class in net.gravitydevelopment.anticheat.util.rule
The conditional rule follows the same syntax as the traditional CS conditional operator.
(CONDITION) ? (TRUE RESULT) : (FALSE RESULT)
Where CONDITION is a statement that will be evaluated as either TRUE or FALSE and the results are actions to be taken for either outcome.
